الآن بما أنّ الـ backend تاعك يخدم، لازم تعطي للـ frontend developer وثيقة واضحة فيها API specification باش يعرف كيف يتعامل مع السيرفر.
الواجهة عادةً تتوثّق بـ REST API doc أو OpenAPI (Swagger)، لكن نقدر نبدأ بواحدة بسيطة:

📌 Product API Documentation
Base URL
http://localhost:3000

1. Get all products

Endpoint: GET /products

Description: يرجّع قائمة بكل المنتجات.

Response Example:

[
  {
    "id": 1,
    "name": "شعير",
    "price": "100.00",
    "quantity": 200
  },
  {
    "id": 2,
    "name": "قمح",
    "price": "150.00",
    "quantity": 300
  }
]

2. Get product by ID

Endpoint: GET /products/:id

Example:

GET /products/1


Response:

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "شعير",
  "price": "100.00",
  "quantity": 200
}

3. Create a new product

Endpoint: POST /products

Headers:

Content-Type: application/json


Body Example:

{
  "name": "شعير",
  "price": 100,
  "quantity": 200
}


Response:

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "شعير",
  "price": "100.00",
  "quantity": 200
}

4. Update a product

Endpoint: PUT /products/:id

Example:

PUT /products/1


Body Example:

{
  "name": "شعير بلدي",
  "price": 120,
  "quantity": 250
}


Response:

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "شعير بلدي",
  "price": "120.00",
  "quantity": 250
}

5. Delete a product

Endpoint: DELETE /products/:id

Example:

DELETE /products/1


Response:

{ "message": "Product deleted successfully" }

